data.description: Totally impressive. Situated on a great fenced lot on a cul-de-sac street close to everything. Move right in and enjoy. Kitchen was expanded and ceiling vaulted with 2 skylights. Everything updated. Replacement windows too. Brick paver front patio, oversized 2 car garage with custom built-in work bench that conveys. So many updates including bamboo flooring throughout main level, new SS kitchen appliances that convey, updated LL full bath, added cabinetry in laundry room, new LL carpet and roof and water heater less than 5 years old. Ready for the discriminating buyer.
